txt.en: Wanted: Extremely sharp claws from the creeping things surrounding Thorenhad. All items should be delivered to the collection box at the outpost in the Trollshaws.
You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
You have not recovered enough extremely sharp claws for the Elves at Thorenhad.
Elves of Rivendell Task: Extremely Sharp Claws
The Elves at Thorenhad desire a delivery of extremely sharp claws to be made to them.
Deliver the extremely sharp claws to the collection box

You have accepted a task to collect extremely sharp claws from the creeping things in the areas surrounding Thorenhad. The items are to be delivered to a collection box. There is a collection box at Thorenhad in the Trollshaws.
Wanted: Extremely sharp claws from the creeping things surrounding Thorenhad.
